Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:19.15,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}踏み込んで覚醒ざめる chasin' the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:59.47,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}唯有你知從我的雙眸迸發出的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:07.68,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}闖進這個世界中覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:19.32,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}俯瞰那專屬於我的渺小世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.28,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}但卻被捏造的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:32.08,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}失焦了我的雙眼 方然覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:42.23,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}衝刺而來的未來 將美好緊握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:51.14,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}追尋各自飛翔的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:03:00.25,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}唯有你知從我的雙眸迸發出的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:05.84,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}開始加速向著我的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:11.54,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}想要更加激昂 更加強大地傳達於你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:19.15,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(150,200)}闖進這個世界中覺醒 chasin' the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給小豬今天的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然還會做這種噩夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班級什麼的 要是沒有就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 你還醒著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛醒過來不久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花要凋謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我把大門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潛入我家的家庭服務器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧 就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 什麼讓人沒辦法的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「直接連結」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Direct Link>
Comment: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個奇蝦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寒武紀時代的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在使用這個「虛擬角色」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(763,655)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換一個不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經習慣這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 這個墊子地…天國是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前作為升級祝賀 增加了存取空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個分辨率下 從一邊到另一邊有15公里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 那也讓我來玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓小春個人化之後 就都是機油和鐵塊了 噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡放上虎式坦克啊 VF109戰鬥機之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 不 要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說今天晚上可能會做噩夢 所以我才睡不著的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做那個夢的話 是做不出「對戰虛擬角色」的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(848,655)}<Duel Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是等等 「虛擬角色」是受心理創傷左右而作成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(489,655)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是沒有心理陰影的人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒禮貌啊 心理陰影我還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 小學遠足的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是哪個某人暈車 在我的膝蓋上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我很抱歉 請不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 乖乖別動 你是枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起以前 小春留宿在我家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把你當枕頭的話 就能睡得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前…那都是很久之前的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力了哦 為了成為「超頻連線者」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(848,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我努力過了 所以能回去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到大家一起玩的那時
Comment: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了 你為什麼哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 三個人都在一個班級裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早 真的是很巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要一直泡在網上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝會要開始了
Comment: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多數諸位 現在正深切感受到期待與不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是 新生的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對陌生的校舍 陌生的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.62,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,非常迷惑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一臉正經在發表演說的人 在另一個世界居然是秩序的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓美國海軍陸戰隊都驚嚇的魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經也和你們有著相同的不安 站在相同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我的內心被她看穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.18,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,一年…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間既是非常龐大 又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間既是非常龐大 又是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請將這一年過的充滿意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的話就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:19.19,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 由生活指導的老師來介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:24.42,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,在學校內使用「神經連結裝置」時的注意事項
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:24.42,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(642,55)}<Neural Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Comment: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新生裡有「超頻連線者」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(711,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她是不是注意到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都看著新生那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連線者」通常都是與替自己安裝程式的「上輩」念同一間學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(182,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 可能性也並非完全沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之去確認下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多帳戶的分發也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在新生正要連接區域網了 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:08:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個又要偷偷摸摸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 你們要去加速世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以開始玩這個遊戲 是因為要告訴你們遊戲是要愉快地玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一起玩就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 小拓就當觀眾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都要使用1點「超頻點數」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(787,655)}<Burst Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就順便看下小千的「對戰虛擬角色」是怎麼樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(680,655)}<Duel Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我要幹些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在那裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就向小千提出對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連接」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Burst Link>
Comment: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個就是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 這個就是小千的「對戰虛擬角色」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(787,655)}<Duel Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字上是顯示著「Lime Bell」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「Lime Bell」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺顏色是不是太亮了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱怨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮮艷度那麼高的顏色很少見的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你是小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 「虛擬角色」是心理陰影的表現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(490,655)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用說出來 我知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個就是小拓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺和形象一樣 與小春不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 果然新生中似乎沒有「超頻連線者」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(846,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 列表中只有\N「Silver Crow」、「Black Lotus」、「Cyan Pile」 還有「Lime Bell」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這4個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:11:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 話說回來 現在我和小春是正在對戰的狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 你知道規則嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致上從小拓那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重點就是 梆梆地贏下對戰 噌噌地賺取「點數」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(971,655)}<Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達到等級10的話就通關了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按這種說法的話感覺是很簡單啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 沒有必殺技之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個我說啊…真是的 畫面的這附近有體力槽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡打開技能列表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 必殺技…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 「香櫞鐘聲」…啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(627,655)}<Citron Call>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說好好把話聽完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必殺技必須要蓄必殺技槽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己受到傷害 或是對對方造成傷害…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還…還有 破壞附近的物體也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒暢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手下一點都不留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 「Lime Bell」的體力沒有減少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工廠舞臺的話 破壞物體的話 應該是會受到傷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是防禦力很高嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想必殺技槽差不多也蓄滿了 應該可以用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 再來一次 「香櫞鐘聲」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(750,655)}<Citron Call>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 不是什麼都沒發生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是幻術之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這個派不上用場的必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 給我一個你的必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是一般的幻覺技能的話 必殺技槽的減少太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不是傷害 也不是弱化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那個鐘戳戳看小春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算這麼幹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,減少得還不夠 再來2次左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？ 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 再對小春使用一次必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「香櫞鐘聲」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Citron Call>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的猜測是正確的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體力槽恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「Lime Bell」 是治療者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治療者？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下不得了了
Comment: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說是治療者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 小拓也大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是會造成大騷動的 絕對不要公開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓武同學是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謠言傳開了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全東京的「超頻連線者」肯定會聚集到杉並區來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(520,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始嘗試拉攏她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治療者那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界誕生以來整整七年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有恢復能力的「超頻連線者」 只出現了2個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(662,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且其中一人無法忍受圍繞著自己展開的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退出了加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 現在除了「Lime Bell」之外 就只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那個人現在是六個王之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王的其中一個？是什麼顏色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 現在有關那個人的事 連名字都不想讓你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不希望你對那個人有哪怕是一絲一毫的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然我是相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會對其他的王有興趣 接受他們的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即便如此 我也無法抑制我的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春雪 你是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今是如此 以後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未來永遠 不會讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離題了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 恢復能力在加速世界就是如此稀有 如此地能發揮作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 倉嶋同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在小拓應該正在告訴她注意不要輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來需要敞開胸襟與她談一次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐與小千的談判啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很那個啊…
Comment: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「軍團」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(623,655)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我和小春是在一個叫「黑暗星雲」的軍團裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(766,655)}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導人是黑雪公主學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果這樣我們三個人就能又像以前一樣在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能回去的吧 大家能回到那個時候的吧
Comment: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩的禮物 如果你有什麼想要的話就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩？旅行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三年級從下週日開始是修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？修學旅行！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的時候 就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說 10天後最先要解決的 就是倉嶋同學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領土戰要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能忍受在這個杉並區上有著其他的「軍團」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(982,655)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在下週的防禦中成功的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為獎勵 我就聽取你的任何一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 好好地想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 果然這才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要直連就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子呼出的氣 能感受到她鼻子呼出的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太差勁了 我太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 回去冷靜地想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新生？
Comment: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死守 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有吾王的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有她的風格…你還真是冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不只有2個人參與領土戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有其他的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事態總有一天會來的 我有這個覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從進入「黑暗星雲」那一天起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,655)}{\fs35}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小千那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是恢復能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不戰鬥 如果能成為自己人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}能回去的吧 大家能回到那個時候的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小拓？你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Comment: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你等那麼久 我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小拓呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才被拿了1分 1比1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不像以前那樣有壓倒性的感覺 但他也在努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不再使用加速的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 校內比賽拿不下第一的話 在大賽上可打不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體有效 勝負已決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個學生 記得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決賽是 紅色 能美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:19:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色 黛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 那個新生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 小拓 做掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小春也來加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 聲音太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前臂有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小拓？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 明明應該是來得及的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不僅被擋開 還被反過來擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連接」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都那樣確認了 為什麼之前都沒顯示出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才確實是說了Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻登出」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,655)}<Burst Out>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面有效 勝負已決
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝者 紅色 能美
Comment: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.36,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:19.19,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.82,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:22.82,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Flashed in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.32,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}It's a 「Burst」 of sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:31.60,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「諦め」がくれた 安楽 沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:34.60,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}いつからだっただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:37.69,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.04,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わらずにいてと願うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:44.70,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わりゆく時に生きる僕ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.87,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}本当の声を…言い得ぬ夢を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:50.16,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}君と繋がった空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.14,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}響かせて！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:56.10,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと強く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:59.43,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:02.75,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「今度こそは…」 つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:06.01,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:09.31,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:12.53,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:15.86,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}歪む世界 走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.10,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:24.70,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「真実」と 加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.36,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們遭受淚水與傷痛煩心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:19.19,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}而我被置身於那亂於無數未來的競爭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.82,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將自身覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:22.82,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}閃現於高空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.32,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}這就是「加速」快感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:31.60,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「放棄」帶來的安樂停滯世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:34.60,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}何時悄然而至的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:37.69,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}恍然間光輝耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.04,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}祈求永恆無變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:44.70,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們卻生活在幻化無常的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.87,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}搭載著吐露的真聲與難以言說的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:50.16,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與你一同展翅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.14,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}讓聲音迴蕩在天際！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:56.10,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加的堅強…用雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:59.43,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將淚水全部抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:02.75,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}喃喃而道「下次一定…」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:06.01,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}不會讓傷痛僅僅成為過往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:09.31,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加快速地…到達你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:12.53,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}即使羽翼已支離破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:15.86,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}仍會奔跑在這個扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.10,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}依循著感覺的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:24.70,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與「真實」一同加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}下一話 Arrestation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}出發旅行的黑雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}留下的春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}被策略籠罩
